overview.en: YOS is a digital certificate issued by the YOOSourcing platform. It is a blockchain-based global trade inter-enterprise communication and procurement collaboration platform. YOS is applied to all payments of the YOOSourcing platform. The YOOSourcing platform paid corporate members provide value support for YOS.
overview.zh: YOS是YOOSourcing平台发行的数字通证，是基于区块链的全球贸易企业间沟通和采购协作平台，YOS应用于YOOSourcing平台的所有支付，YOOSourcing平台付费企业会员为YOS提供价值支撑。
